title: La Huerta del Chef
description: A hostal restaurant serving breakfast and baked goods. Integral bread Tuesday flaxseed and sweet tofu (soy cheese), gluten (wheat protein), natural jams, borojo jelly, dulce de leche coconut, peanut butter and sesame (tahini), granola, cookies of flaxseed, sunflower seeds, whole-wheat flour per pound and different you medicinal.
